# Voice-reference corpus prose + derived signal cache.
# - The YAML metadata + README are committed (schema + provenance).
# - The passage .txt files are NOT committed: a mix of PG public-domain
#   excerpts, research-fair-use Reddit/HF dataset prose, and LLM-generated
#   outputs with varying license posture. Reproducible via the lab/scripts
#   extractors (see data/voice-references/README.md).
# - The signal cache is derived from passages + YAML, SHA-256-keyed,
#   rebuilds on demand via `uv run python -m owtn.voice.tools rebuild-cache`.
data/voice-references/passages/
data/voice-references-stylometric.cache.json

